    jQuery(document).ready(
            function () {
                jQuery.ajax(nga.paths.getPath("SERVICES") + ".getEventsByDate.json", {
                    async: true,
                    type: "GET",
                    dataType: "json",
                    cache: false,
                    success: function (data) {
                        var date = new Date(data.results.date);

                        var eventCount = 0;
                        var counter = 0;
                        var eventHtml = "";

                        eventHtml += "<dl><dt>Today at the NGA</dt><dd>" + $.datepicker.formatDate( "MM dd, yy", date) + "</dd></dl>";

                        if((date.getDate() == 25 && date.getMonth()==11) || (date.getDate() == 1 && date.getMonth()==0)){
                            eventHtml += "<dl><dd>The Gallery is closed today.</dd></dl>";
                        }else if(false){
                            eventHtml += "<dl><dd>The Gallery is closed today and all events cancelled.</dd></dl>";
                        }else{
                            var times =data.results.times;
                            if(times.length == 0){
                                eventHtml += "<dl><dd>There are no events scheduled for this date.</dd></dl>";
                            }

                            for(var key = 0; key < times.length; key++){
                                var time = times[key];


                                var eventTime = time.time.match(/(\d+)(?::(\d\d))?\s*(P?)/);
                                var hours = eventTime[3] && eventTime[1]!= "12"?(parseInt(eventTime[1]) + 12):eventTime[1];
                                var minutes = eventTime[2];
                                var eventDate = new Date(data.results.date.substr(0, 11) + hours+":" + minutes );
                                for(var i = 0;  i < time.event.length; i++){
                                    counter++;
                                    if(eventCount == 3 || (date > eventDate  && data.totalcount >= counter+3)) {
                                        continue;
                                    };
                                    var event = time.event[i];
                                    eventHtml += "<dl>";
                                    eventHtml += "<dt>" + time.time  + "</dt>";
                                    eventHtml += "<dd>" + event.category + "</dd>";
                                    eventHtml += "<dd><a href=\"" + event.path + "\">" + event.title + "</a></dd></dl>";
                                    eventCount++;
                                };

                            };
                        };
                        eventHtml += "<dl><dd><a href=\"/content/ngaweb/calendar.html\">all events</a></dd></dl>";
                        jQuery(".eventfeed").append(eventHtml);

                    },
                    error: function (xhr, status, err) {
                        console.log("dynamically generated events error: ", err);
                    }
                });
            });
</script></div>
